Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.nanoservice.interfaces

Interface MethodExecutor

Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface
public interface MethodExecutor

This interface is an internal interface for NanoServiceFactory implementation. When any pluggable processing class was installed into Nano service, wrapper class will be created for it. This wrapper must implements this interface to process HTTP-requests to it.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
NanoService, NanoServiceFactory

    • execute

      int execute​(QueryType type, char[] path, char[] query, com.sun.net.httpserver.Headers requestHeaders, com.sun.net.httpserver.Headers responseHeaders, java.io.InputStream is, java.io.OutputStream os) throws java.io.IOException, ContentException, FlowException, EnvironmentException

      Process HTTP request and return HTTP response code

      Parameters:
      type - query type
      path - path from browser address string
      query - query from browser address string
      requestHeaders - list of request headers from HTTP request
      responseHeaders - list of HTTP headers for HTTP response
      is - request body
      os - stream for response body
      Returns:
      HTTP response code
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - on any I/O errors
      ContentException - on any content errors
      FlowException - on any flow errors
      EnvironmentException - in any environment errors
